title: Marvel Comics Introduces a Brand New Team - The Dark Guardians with a Deadly Mission
body:
Marvel Comics Introduces a Brand New Team – The Dark Guardians with a Deadly Mission

**Warning Spoilers for Guardians of the Galaxy #2**

Marvel Comics introduced a brand new team to the Marvel Universe in the form of the Dark Guardians in the pages of Guardians of the Galaxy #2 by Donny Cates and Geoff Shaw.

The team consists of Starfox, who is pulling off his best Charles Xavier impression, Gladiator, Cosmic Ghost Rider, Nebula, and Wraith or Zak-Del.

Given the cover preview…
